data.description: This adorable tri-level boosts a welcoming Livingroom upon entry. Natural light fills the space, making it feel airy and inviting. Eat-in kitchen with a walk out to the large fenced backyard, makes this home optimal for entertaining. Open concept stairs both up and down. The top level houses a master bedroom, plus one additional bedroom and fully redone bathrooms, with stunning vanity and LVP flooring. The lower living area has built-in bookcases, perfect for those avid readers looking for their own personal library space. The downstairs area also hosts a bedroom and a half bath, along with the laundry area. An oversized garage is perfect for those looking for space for a workshop or craft area. This wonderful home is just waiting for its next adventure.
